thread.title_full: Otticanet recensione scritta da Jay Brumm

author: Jay Brumm
title: Jay Brumm
text: Otticanet had the frames I saw at my optometrist for $530 on their site for $170! And I got 5% more off that so I only paid $160. They are located in Italy and I am in California US and it only took 4 days to ship them to me. Amazing buying experience and I will definitely order again
